**Backup:** `C:\Users\PLUTO\openclaw_config\openclaw.json.bak4`

- `models.providers.ollama.models` array replaced: removed gemma3:12b, gemma3:12b-fc, old qwen2.5-coder/gpt-oss entries. New array: gpt-oss:20b, qwen2.5-coder:14b, qwen3-vl:8b (all with `name` field — required by OpenClaw schema)
