## RTL-058 Phase 2 — Routing Logging Infrastructure (2026-03-10)

### Overview

Full routing feedback logging pipeline: Chroma server standup (Prompt 1) + logging shim service (Prompt 2). Zuberi's model-router skill can now log every discipline routing decision to both CXDB (authoritative, append-only) and Chroma (semantic index with vector search).

### Prompt 1: Chroma Server on CEG

| Item | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Service | `chroma-server.service` (user systemd) |
| Binary | `/opt/zuberi/trading/venv/bin/chroma` (chromadb 1.5.2) |
| Listen | `100.100.101.1:8000` (Tailscale IP) |
| Data dir | `/opt/zuberi/data/chroma-server/` |
| API version | v2 only (v1 deprecated) |
| Collection | `router_records` (ID `7bc8c60b-dd6d-463a-9a66-c58f64a6e72e`) |
| Embedding model | all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (384 dims, auto via onnxruntime in Python client) |
| Key constraint | REST v2 API requires precomputed embeddings — use `chromadb.HttpClient` Python client, NOT raw curl |

### Prompt 2: Routing Logging Shim on CEG

| Item | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Service | `routing-shim.service` (user systemd) |
| Binary | `/opt/zuberi/trading/venv/bin/python /opt/zuberi/services/routing-shim/main.py` |
| Framework | FastAPI 0.135.1 + uvicorn 0.41.0 |
| Listen | `100.100.101.1:8100` (Tailscale IP) |
| Deps installed | `fastapi`, `starlette` (into trading venv) |

**Endpoints:**

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| GET | `/health` | Probes CXDB + Chroma, returns `{status, cxdb, chroma}` |
| POST | `/log` | Logs routing decision to CXDB (authoritative) then Chroma (best-effort) |

**POST /log request:**
```json
{
  "task_type": "code|image|tool_call|deep_analysis|general",
  "model_used": "qwen2.5-coder:14b",
  "input_summary": "Brief text describing the task (used for Chroma embedding)",
  "tool_flag": false,
  "think_flag": false,
  "latency_ms": 2500,
  "success": true,
  "error_text": null
}
```

**POST /log response:**
```json
{
  "ok": true,
  "cxdb_turn_id": 29,
  "chroma_id": "rt-29-1773203924",
  "error": null
}
```

**CXDB details:**
- Context ID: **11** (dedicated routing log context)
- Type: `zuberi.routing.Record` v1 (registered in `bundle_zuberi-routing-2026-03.json`)
- Schema: `{role: "system", text: "pipe-delimited fields"}` — matches CXDB's `{role, text}` pattern
- Text format: `task_type=X | model=Y | tool=Z | think=Z | success=Z | latency_ms=N | summary=... | ts=ISO8601`
- `turn_id` is the authoritative CXDB reference

**Chroma details:**
- Collection: `router_records`
- Document: `input_summary` text (auto-embedded by Python client)
- ID format: `rt-{cxdb_turn_id}-{unix_timestamp}`
- Metadata: `task_type`, `model_used`, `tool_flag`, `think_flag`, `success`, `latency_ms`, `cxdb_turn_id`, `timestamp`
- Failure is non-fatal — CXDB write must succeed, Chroma is best-effort

**Type registry:**
- Bundle file: `/opt/zuberi/docker/cxdb/registry/bundle_zuberi-routing-2026-03.json`
- Copied into CXDB container via `docker cp` to `/data/registry/`
- CXDB requires container restart to pick up new registry bundles

### OBSTACLES LOG

| # | Obstacle | Resolution | Impact |
|---|----------|------------|--------|
| 1 | CXDB reads failed with "type descriptor" error after adding registry bundle | `docker restart cxdb` — container needed restart to pick up new registry files | CXDB type registry is file-based, not hot-reloaded |
| 2 | CXDB Docker container binds to Tailscale IP (100.100.101.1), not 127.0.0.1 | Use `100.100.101.1:9010` for all CXDB access from CEG | Port mapping: `100.100.101.1:9010->80/tcp` |
| 3 | Chroma v2 REST API requires precomputed embeddings for add/query | Use `chromadb.HttpClient` Python client (handles embedding via onnxruntime) | Cannot use raw curl for Chroma writes — must go through Python client |
| 4 | No FastAPI in trading venv | `pip install fastapi` — installed FastAPI 0.135.1 + Starlette 0.52.1 | Two new packages in trading venv |
| 5 | Port 8100 "address in use" on first systemd start | Killed stale manual test process, restarted service | One-time issue from smoke testing |

### Validation Results

| Check | Result |
|-------|--------|
| Chroma server healthy | ✅ `systemctl --user status chroma-server` — active (running) |
| Routing shim healthy | ✅ `systemctl --user status routing-shim` — active (running) |
| GET /health from CEG | ✅ `{"status":"ok","cxdb":"ok","chroma":"ok"}` |
| GET /health from KILO (Tailscale) | ✅ Same response over Tailscale |
| POST /log (code task) | ✅ turn_id=29, chroma_id=rt-29-1773203924 |
| POST /log (image task from KILO) | ✅ turn_id=30, chroma_id=rt-30-1773204068 |
| POST /log (tool_call + error) | ✅ turn_id=31, chroma_id=rt-31-1773204093 |
| CXDB read-back context 11 | ✅ All 3 records decoded with full data |
| Chroma semantic query | ✅ "image analysis" → image task ranked #1 (dist 1.55) over code task (dist 1.88) |
| Linger enabled (survives logout) | ✅ Already enabled from previous setup |

